    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>As part of the Catalysts for Change project SEEDs, funded by the Queen’s Nursing Institute Scotland (QNIS) in partnership with The National Lottery Community Fund, community nurses in Edinburgh and students at Queen Margaret University (QMU) were encouraged to share their stories of working through the pandemic for a new collection of writing recently launched at the 13th annual Portobello Book festival.</p>]]></Value>
